OL,3,CThousands march through London to
OL,4,Cdemand cleaner water
OL,6,FThousands of people have marched
OL,7,Fthrough London to demand tougher
OL,8,Faction on keeping the UK's rivers and
OL,9,Fseas clean.
OL,11,FA range of groups, including River
OL,12,FAction, Greenpeace, the Wildlife
OL,13,FTrusts and British Rowing, took to the
OL,14,Fstreets for for the campaign amid a
OL,15,Fgrowing water quality crisis in the UK.
OL,17,FMany wearing blue to form a mass human
OL,18,Friver, joined by many high-profile
OL,19,Fcampaigners.
