OL,3,CThousands march through London to
OL,4,Cdemand cleaner water
OL,6,FThe March for Clean Water ended with a
OL,7,Frally at Westminster.
OL,9,FSouthern Water says it has an
OL,10,Fambitious investment plan for the next
OL,11,Ffive years to protect the environment,
OL,12,Fand improve water supply. The cost
OL,13,Fborne by both shareholders and
OL,14,Fcustomers.
OL,16,FThe government says it has launched
OL,17,Fthe biggest review of the water sector
OL,18,Fsince privatisation and it plans new
OL,19,Fpowers to curb bonuses for water
OL,20,Fbosses and bring criminal charges
OL,21,Fagainst persistent law breakers.
