OL,3,CThousands march through London to
OL,4,Cdemand cleaner water
OL,6,FEnvironmental activist and singer
OL,7,FFeargal Sharkey, TV presenter Chris
OL,8,FPackham and adventurer Bear Grylls
OL,9,Fwere among those at the event.
OL,11,FThe campaign is calling for an
OL,12,Fimmediate root and branch review of
OL,13,Fthe regulator Ofwat and the
OL,14,FEnvironment Agency, the stricter
OL,15,Fenforcement of existing laws and
OL,16,Fregulations on water pollution and
OL,17,Fensuring all polluting industries
OL,18,Finvest in upgrading infrastructure,
OL,19,Freducing water wastage and leakage and
OL,20,Fhelping farmers restore habitats.
