OL,3,CThousands march through London to
OL,4,Cdemand cleaner water
OL,6,FA Water UK spokesperson said: "The
OL,7,FMarch for Clean Water is right to
OL,8,Fdemand change and we support its aims.
OL,9,FWe agree that the system is not
OL,10,Fworking. It is too complicated, too
OL,11,Fslow and is not delivering for people
OL,12,For the environment.
OL,14,F"No sewage spill is ever acceptable,
OL,15,Fand water companies want to invest a
OL,16,Frecord #108 billion to ensure the
OL,17,Fsecurity of our water supply in the
OL,18,Ffuture and end sewage entering our
OL,19,Frivers and seas.
