OL,6,F"Ofwat have proposed cutting this by
OL,7,F#20 billion. As a direct result, more
OL,8,Fhousing will be blocked, the recovery
OL,9,Fof our rivers will be slower, and we
OL,10,Fwill fail to deal with the water
OL,11,Fshortages we know are coming.
OL,13,F"We cannot delay upgrading and
OL,14,Fexpanding vital infrastructure any
OL,15,Flonger and need Ofwat to reconsider
OL,16,Fits approach."
